  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2436410/extras/3ab4c4490a4ce8e3ddf8113dd861aeb2.avif?t=1756392674\" width=396 height=127 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2436410/extras/94a6b128470eb3dc745d6cc5f88d01ea.avif?t=1756392674\" width=614 height=154 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dive into a world shaped by Charlie’s fears.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore magical places and meet quirky characters. Help them solve their strange problems through fun puzzles!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You’ll need to carefully observe your surroundings and chat with the residents of Asfalia to uncover the mystery behind the missing puppies!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The dialogues are full of humor, wit, and cultural references, making the adventure just as enjoyable for older players. That’s right—Asfalia is for everyone!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2436410/extras/c8d250384315435faee710d2e59c85d6.poster.avif?t=1756392674\" width=780 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2436410/extras/c8d250384315435faee710d2e59c85d6.webm?t=1756392674\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2436410/extras/c8d250384315435faee710d2e59c85d6.mp4?t=1756392674\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2436410/extras/56d0c0b6cd0c6f3a719731095702bc44.avif?t=1756392674\" width=614 height=154 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Asfalia is designed for children aged 7 and up, as well as adults curious to experience a humorous adventure.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The puzzles are fun and easy to solve, and the intuitive controls make the game easy to pick up. Asfalia is fully playable with a mouse or a gamepad, and it’s perfectly compatible with the Steam Deck. It’s ideal for long trips with kids: a game that can be enjoyed anywhere, with ease!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2436410/extras/5adcdd0fc7c9215438961d4fa21d5c66.avif?t=1756392674\" width=614 height=154 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After a powerful storm, Charlie’s puppies get scared and run into the forest. While trying to find them, Charlie ends up in a world where the stars have vanished. Can you uncover the mystery behind their disappearance?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Asfalia is a hand-painted world with a unique and enchanting style. It’s a whimsical universe filled with adorable and mischievous characters, inspired by <i>Alice in Wonderland</i>, <i>Inside Out</i>, and <i>The Little Prince</i>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2436410/extras/39298d7392731562e9d5763b68bfa5e9.avif?t=1756392674\" width=614 height=154 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A cheese-loving knife, a cleaning-obsessed marquis, an adventurous ghost... The world of Asfalia is packed with characters who are as silly as they are lovable.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With professional voice acting in French and English, energetic performances, and a rich soundscape, you’ll be immersed in a lively and charming adventure.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2436410/extras/fc30eeae558a0da51941b97ad3a911f0.poster.avif?t=1756392674\" width=780 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2436410/extras/fc30eeae558a0da51941b97ad3a911f0.webm?t=1756392674\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2436410/extras/fc30eeae558a0da51941b97ad3a911f0.mp4?t=1756392674\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2436410/extras/a803e5e9f0b862f9971825a658e37688.avif?t=1756392674\" width=614 height=154 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Asfalia is bursting with lighthearted and delightful puzzles that are never too tricky.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Can you rebuild a cat statue? Take on the challenges of mischievous vultures? Find a way to restore courage to a frightened ghost?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2436410/extras/7df08588f06c051fa15fb2b5cceff363.avif?t=1756392674\" width=614 height=154 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Interact with your environment to expand your sticker collection. Some of them are very well hidden... ;)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2436410/extras/08e9c7a0952c5e1363a3029feadaca0d.poster.avif?t=1756392674\" width=780 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2436410/extras/08e9c7a0952c5e1363a3029feadaca0d.webm?t=1756392674\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2436410/extras/08e9c7a0952c5e1363a3029feadaca0d.mp4?t=1756392674\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2436410/extras/2c6b1ee28c72240336a707710c83bd32.avif?t=1756392674\" width=614 height=154 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In short, Asfalia is a world filled with charming and funny characters, wrapped in an engaging narrative.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Asfalia: Panic at the Mansion </i>is the second adventure in the Asfalia universe, following <i>Asfalia: The Cranky Volcano</i> — and more adventures are on the way.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A vibrant world awaits… Let’s go to Asfalia!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2436410/extras/0d48e9d01fe0c03fbcaf933483f3b92d.avif?t=1756392674\" width=396 height=127 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2436410/extras/3ab4c4490a4ce8e3ddf8113dd861aeb2.avif?t=1756392674\" width=396 height=127 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2436410/extras/94a6b128470eb3dc745d6cc5f88d01ea.avif?t=1756392674\" width=614 height=154 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dive into a world shaped by Charlie’s fears.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore magical places and meet quirky characters. Help them solve their strange problems through fun puzzles!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You’ll need to carefully observe your surroundings and chat with the residents of Asfalia to uncover the mystery behind the missing puppies!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The dialogues are full of humor, wit, and cultural references, making the adventure just as enjoyable for older players. That’s right—Asfalia is for everyone!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2436410/extras/c8d250384315435faee710d2e59c85d6.poster.avif?t=1756392674\" width=780 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2436410/extras/c8d250384315435faee710d2e59c85d6.webm?t=1756392674\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2436410/extras/c8d250384315435faee710d2e59c85d6.mp4?t=1756392674\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam