nture.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2436410/extras/fc30eeae558a0da51941b97ad3a911f0.poster.avif?t=1756392674\" width=780 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2436410/extras/fc30eeae558a0da51941b97ad3a911f0.webm?t=1756392674\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2436410/extras/fc30eeae558a0da51941b97ad3a911f0.mp4?t=1756392674\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2436410/extras/a803e5e9f0b862f9971825a658e37688.avif?t=1756392674\" width=614 height=154 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Asfalia is bursting with lighthearted and delightful puzzles that are never too tricky.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Can you rebuild a cat statue? Take on the challenges of mischievous vultures? Find a way to restore courage to a frightened ghost?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2436410/extras/7df08588f06c051fa15fb2b5cceff363.avif?t=1756392674\" width=614 height=154 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Interact with your environment to expand your sticker collection. Some of them are very well hidden... ;)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2436410/extras/08e9c7a0952c5e1363a3029feadaca0d.poster.avif?t=1756392674\" width=780 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared